  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Operating acute kidney injury electronic alert in geriatric wards; Acute authenticity
      evaluation of acute kidney injury electronic alert; To explore the clinical value of
      electronic alert for acute kidney injury prevention and treatment in geriatric wards.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
