    <description>The e-alert system was developed by the divisions of Nephrology and Information Management of Guangdong Provincial People's Hospital (Patent Application 201610001950.5). The alert system made a diagnosis of acute kidney injury according to Kidney Disease: Improving Global Outcomes criteria. Then, the doctor receives an alert of acute kidney injury.</description>
